  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Bleeding peptic ulcer

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patient is: &lt; 18 years of age

          -  Patient is unable to consent

          -  Patient is contraindicated to undergo endoscopy

          -  Patient has: coagulopathy, altered post surgical anatomy of the stomach, previously
             placed intrahepatic portosystemic shunt

          -  Patient is pregnant or lactating

          -  Patinet has an INR &gt; 2.5
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
